00:36:13.971 --> 00:36:15.573 line:95%,end
after week?

00:36:15.640 --> 00:36:17.341 line:95%,end
<i>I am fired up.</i>

00:36:17.408 --> 00:36:19.810 line:95%,end
Those girls were outstanding.

