Where Have All the Children Gone?

00:37:02.520 --> 00:37:06.257 line:95%,end
NARRATOR: <i>The creaking silence of age</i>

00:37:06.324 --> 00:37:08.459 line:95%,end
<i>echoes through the streets.</i>

