<i>All of the children once</i>
<i>running around have evacuated.</i>

00:37:13.497 --> 00:37:17.101 line:95%,end
<i>Or maybe they just disappeared.</i>

00:37:18.636 --> 00:37:21.706 line:95%,end
<i>Just yesterday,</i>
<i>they were tying ribbons in trees</i>

00:37:21.772 --> 00:37:24.208 line:95%,end
<i>and swinging from the branches.</i>

00:37:24.609 --> 00:37:29.680 line:95%,end
<i>They were leaping over hot coals</i>
<i>and swooning at anything.</i>

00:37:30.681 --> 00:37:35.119 line:95%,end
<i>Where have all the children gone?</i>

00:37:36.354 --> 00:37:39.490 line:95%,end
<i>Who remain wander around</i>

00:37:39.557 --> 00:37:43.628 line:95%,end
<i>like abandoned children</i>
<i>in shopping malls.</i>

00:37:44.262 --> 00:37:48.165 line:95%,end
<i>Maybe this is just a dream.</i>

00:37:49.000 --> 00:37:53.404 line:95%,end
<i>Maybe we are sleeping in rooms</i>

00:37:53.471 --> 00:37:57.041 line:95%,end
