00:37:57.108 --> 00:37:59.944 line:95%,end
<i>If we put our ears to those shelves</i>

00:38:00.011 --> 00:38:03.481 line:95%,end
<i>emptied by the fingers of fathers</i>

00:38:03.547 --> 00:38:06.817 line:95%,end
<i>to the flesh</i>
<i>of their sons and daughters.</i>

